  }, "v12"), mdx("p", null, "\u0110\u1ED1i v\u1EDBi anh ch\u1ECB em c\u0169ng th\u1EBF. V\xEC anh ch\u1ECB em r\u1EA5t mong m\u1ECFi nh\u1EADn \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c c\xE1c \xE2n t\u1EE9 thi\xEAng li\xEAng n\xEAn h\xE3y t\xECm \xE2n t\u1EE9 n\xE0o c\xF3 th\u1EC3 g\xE2y d\u1EF1ng h\u1ED9i th\xE1nh th\xEAm l\u1EDBn m\u1EA1nh. "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v13"
  }, "v13"), mdx("p", null, "Ng\u01B0\u1EDDi \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c \xE2n t\u1EE9 n\xF3i ng\xF4n ng\u1EEF l\u1EA1 n\xEAn c\u1EA7u xin c\xF3 \xE2n t\u1EE9 di\u1EC5n gi\u1EA3i ng\xF4n ng\u1EEF \u1EA5y. "), mdx("h6", {
